'''傑克·韋恩·希克馬'''（{{lang-en|Jack Wayne Sikma}}，{{bd|1955年|11月14日||}}），[[美國|美國]]前職業[[篮球|篮球]]運動員，司职中锋/大前锋。曾效力於[[國家籃球協會|國家籃球協會]]（NBA）的[[西雅圖超音速|西雅圖超音速]]（[[奧克拉荷馬雷霆|奧克拉荷馬雷霆]]前身）及[[密爾瓦基公鹿|密爾瓦基公鹿]]。2019年入選[[籃球名人堂|奈史密斯籃球名人紀念堂]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 職業生涯 ===
希克馬於{{le|1977年NBA选秀|1977 NBA Draft}}中第一輪第8順位被[[西雅圖超音速|西雅圖超音速]]選中<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.nytimes.com/1978/05/26/archives/sikma-is-a-surprise-out-of-nowhere-sonic-star-comes-out-of-nowhere.html|title = Sikora is a Surprise Out of Nowhere|newspaper = The New York Times|date = 1978-05-26|accessdate = 2020-12-02|archive-date = 2019-03-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327100554/https://www.nytimes.com/1978/05/26/archives/sikma-is-a-surprise-out-of-nowhere-sonic-star-comes-out-of-nowhere.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，並參與過超音速隊史最輝煌的時期之一。希克馬在其新秀球季以出賽80場、場均10.7分8.3籃板的表現入選年度新秀陣容，該年超音速隊打進了NBA總決賽，在七場比賽中輸給了[[華盛頓子彈|華盛頓子彈]]隊。第二個賽季，即1978-1979年，希克馬場均貢獻15.6分和12.4個籃板，並入選了全明星賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/teams/SEA/1978.html|title=1977-78 Seattle SuperSonics Roster and Stats|website=Basketball-Reference.com|accessdate=2020-12-02|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922081305/https://www.basketball-reference.com/teams/SEA/1978.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當年超音速隊再次與子彈隊於總決賽碰頭，超音速隊扳回一城，以4-1贏得系列賽，獲得隊史至今唯一一座NBA冠軍盃<ref name="Sonics Defeat Bullets">{{Cite news| url=https://www.nytimes.com/1979/05/30/archives/sonics-defeat-bullets-102102-after-4-quarters-sonics-at-first-and.html| title=Sonics Defeat Bullets| newspaper=The New York Times| date=1979-05-30| accessdate=2020-12-02| archive-date=2019-03-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327122424/https://www.nytimes.com/1979/05/30/archives/sonics-defeat-bullets-102102-after-4-quarters-sonics-at-first-and.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/teams/SEA/1979.html|title=1978-79 Seattle SuperSonics Roster and Stats|website=Basketball-Reference.com|accessdate=2020-12-02|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102124648/https://www.basketball-reference.com/teams/SEA/1979.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

從1979年到1985年，希克馬連續7年入選全明星賽。但在超音速隊連續缺席了兩年的季后賽之後，希克馬向球隊要求交易<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1986-05-30-8602100035-story.html | title=Bulls Center Attention on Sonics' Sikma | accessdate=2020-12-02 | archive-date=2019-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111143203/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1986-05-30-8602100035-story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1986年，超音速將希克馬與1988年的第二輪選秀權交易至[[密爾沃基雄鹿|密爾沃基雄鹿]]隊，以換取[[奥尔顿·利斯特|奥尔顿·利斯特]]和雄鹿的1987年及1989年的第一輪選秀權<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://articles.latimes.com/1986-07-02/sports/sp-468_1_milwaukee-bucks|title = Sikma Traded to Bucks for Lister|newspaper = Los Angeles Times|date = 1986-07-02|accessdate = 2020-12-02|archive-date = 2016-03-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309182045/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-07-02/sports/sp-468_1_milwaukee-bucks|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他於密爾沃基打了5個球季，最終在1990-91年賽季結束後宣布退休。總共14年的職業生涯場均15.6分9.8籃板。1992年11月21日，杰克·希克马的43号球衣被超音速退役。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/sonics/news/retired_jerseys_sikma.html|title=SONICS: Sonics Retired Jerseys: Jack Sikma|website=www.nba.com|accessdate=2020-12-02|archive-date=2019-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190103110649/http://www.nba.com/sonics/news/retired_jerseys_sikma.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年4月6日，他入選了[[奈史密斯籃球名人紀念堂|奈史密斯籃球名人紀念堂]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.twincities.com/2019/04/06/jack-sikma-hall-of-fame-timberwolves-nba-final-four/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407141423/https://www.twincities.com/2019/04/06/jack-sikma-hall-of-fame-timberwolves-nba-final-four/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 執教 ===
2003年到2007年，希克馬擔任西雅圖超音速隊的助理教練。

2007年6月，希克馬被休斯頓火箭隊聘為教練[[里克·阿德爾曼|里克·阿德爾曼]]的助理教練；在[[姚明|姚明]]效力休斯頓火箭隊的時候，希格瑪曾經作為姚明的全職中鋒教練，給與了不少技術方面的指導<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chron.com/sports/rockets/article/Adelman-adds-Sikma-three-others-to-Rockets-staff-1805315.php|title=Adelman adds Sikma, three others to Rockets' staff|first1=Jonathan|last1=Feigen|first2=Houston|last2=Chronicle|date=June 20, 2007|website=Houston Chronicle|accessdate=2020-12-02|archive-date=2019-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410231819/https://www.chron.com/sports/rockets/article/Adelman-adds-Sikma-three-others-to-Rockets-staff-1805315.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年12月6日，他再次被里克·阿德爾曼任命為助理教練（明尼蘇達森林狼隊）<ref name="wolves">{{cite web|publisher=[[Minnesota_Timberwolves|Minnesota Timberwolves]]|url=http://www.nba.com/timberwolves/news/basketball_coaching_staffs_announcement_111207.html|title=Wolves Announce Basketball and Coaching Staffs|date=December 6, 2011|accessdate=2020-12-02|archive-date=2019-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410231853/https://www.nba.com/timberwolves/news/basketball_coaching_staffs_announcement_111207.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

從2017年開始擔任[[多倫多猛龍隊|多倫多猛龍隊]]的教練顧問，特別是與中鋒[[约纳斯·瓦兰丘纳斯|约纳斯·瓦兰丘纳斯]]合作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/sports/basketball/2017/02/07/raptors-look-extend-valanciunass-comfort-spot.html|title=Raptors look to extend Valanciunas's comfort spot - The Star|website=thestar.com|accessdate=2020-12-02|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327085858/https://www.thestar.com/sports/basketball/2017/02/07/raptors-look-extend-valanciunass-comfort-spot.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 技术特点 ==
儘管作為中鋒，希克馬出色的投籃能力和非凡的準度使他能夠在禁區之外發揮作用，其絕技又被稱爲“Sikma move”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dongtw.com/sports/nba/20190915/1000923.html |title=名人堂：Jack Sikma的後轉身技術爲其鋪平入選之路 |access-date=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2021-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510220233/https://www.dongtw.com/sports/nba/20190915/1000923.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這項技術被稱為是NBA夢幻舞步的開端。

